Package: edamamore
Title: R Interface to the Edamam Recipe API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Shreya", "Ravilla", email = "shreya.ravilla248", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    person("Aiden", "Kelly", email = "aqkelly@calpoly.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    person("Josh", "Rowe", email = "jsrowe@calpoly.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The edamamore package provides a set of functions to access and query the Edamam Recipe API, allowing users to search for recipes, filter by various criteria, and adjust the recipe ingredients and quantities to their liking. The package is designed to simplify the process of finding and customizing recipes for different dietary needs and preferences.
